Zibo Configuration:
-------------------
smarty.compile.directory
smarty.plugin.[name]

Updating Smarty
---------------
- rename class from file names so you get Smarty.php, Smarty_Compiler.php and Config_File.php
- in Smarty.php, change the variable $compiler_file from 'Smarty_Compiler.class.php' to 'Smarty_Compiler.php' (around line 386)